00:25:51,603 --> 00:25:53,800
 Take my hand. 

295
00:25:55,890 --> 00:25:58,523
 It must be because of my brother. 

296
00:26:00,070 --> 00:26:02,070
It was something I really wanted to see,

297
00:26:02,070 --> 00:26:04,870
