00:26:28,070 --> 00:26:29,780
That's right.

306
00:26:30,303 --> 00:26:32,456
I did that.

307
00:26:37,270 --> 00:26:41,003
The greatest respect for those who left first is

308
00:26:41,003 --> 00:26:43,540
to live life fully.

309
00:26:44,103 --> 00:26:48,136
