310
00:26:48,136 --> 00:26:51,736
they still become a part of my life, as if they are living with us.

311
00:26:57,930 --> 00:27:01,952
So, we are restoring everything to its original state now. Okay?

312
00:27:03,843 --> 00:27:06,136
What should I do and how?

