364
00:30:41,065 --> 00:30:44,198
I wondered why I ended up like this.

365
00:30:44,198 --> 00:30:46,675
It's because I take after you.

366
00:30:49,898 --> 00:30:52,691
Now stop blaming yourself...

367
00:30:53,532 --> 00:30:55,458
