00:32:20,965 --> 00:32:24,398
Well, like me, when someone is injured by a crime or accident,

388
00:32:24,398 --> 00:32:28,365
it's like restoring the appearance from before the injury.

389
00:32:28,365 --> 00:32:30,732
Although scars like these have remained,

390
00:32:30,732 --> 00:32:35,865
plastic surgery was the operation that prevented me from losing myself.

391
00:32:36,932 --> 00:32:39,038
   

392
00:32:39,038 --> 00:32:42,732
Well, this is it!

393
00:32:42,732 --> 00:32:45,398
Plastic surgery that enables one to regain their form before the injury;

394
00:32:45,398 --> 00:32:47,665
restorative plastic surgery.

395
00:32:47,665 --> 00:32:51,498
Could it be called an operation journey to find the lost self?

396
00:32:51,498 --> 00:32:54,698
Up until now, you've only treated cases with a cosmetic inclination,

397
00:32:54,698 --> 00:32:56,598
but now you intend to treat patients

398
00:32:56,598 --> 00:32:59,263
in need of surgery due to trauma or illness as well?

