00:33:54,497 --> 00:33:56,332
The graft is good.

418
00:33:56,332 --> 00:33:58,498
Moisturizing is the most important thing,

419
00:33:58,498 --> 00:34:01,018
so please apply the ointment regularly.

420
00:34:01,018 --> 00:34:03,865
And as for scar treatment,

421
00:34:03,865 --> 00:34:07,131
let's check the progress and revisit it at your next appointment.

